## QuranReaderPro Environment Variables
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your credentials.
#
# 1) Create a free Postgres database on Neon: https://neon.tech/
# 2) In your Neon project, copy the connection string and paste below.
#    It usually looks like:
#    postgresql://<USER>:<PASSWORD>@<HOST>:<PORT>/<DATABASE>
#
# Mandatory: database connection string
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE"

# Optional: override the default port (5000) used by the Express server
# PORT=5000

